++## Summary
++
++**Files created:**
++- `src/proctor/triggers/scheduler.py` — `SchedulerTrigger` class implementing the `Trigger` ABC
++- `tests/test_triggers/test_scheduler.py` — 26 tests (19 pass, 7 skip on trio)
++
